md:
giải nghĩa từ "agrees" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* agrees (verb) : đồng ý, chấp thuận
	+ Example: "I agrees with you that we should go to the movies tonight."
	+ Related words: agreement, agreeable, disagree

* agrees (third person singular present of agree) : (anh/chị/cô ấy) đồng ý
	+ Example: "He agrees with me that we should start the project now."
	+ Related words: agreement, agreeable, disagree

* agrees (plural noun) : các thỏa thuận
	+ Example: "The two companies have reached several agrees on the terms of the contract."
	+ Related words: agreement, agreeable, disagree
